# Hotspot AI — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A **multi-agent Predictive Engineering Intelligence Platform** that connects to any public GitHub repo, analyzes its codebase health using 7 specialized AI agents, predicts which components will fail in the next 90 days, and generates a CEO-friendly business impact report.

