## Features

1. **🏠 Home Page** — Enter any GitHub repo URL, click Analyze
2. **📊 Dashboard** — Health scores, commit charts, bug stats, risk forecast 
3. **🔍 Code Review** — Side-by-side diff viewer + AI-powered code analysis with explanations
4. **📋 CEO Report** — Business-impact report in plain English + email to CEO button
5. **⏳ Live Progress** — Real-time SSE streaming shows which agent is working

## How to Run

### Backend
```bash
cd d:\DESKTOP\HOTSPOT-AI\backend
py -3.14 main.py
# Runs on http://localhost:8000
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd d:\DESKTOP\HOTSPOT-AI\frontend
npx vite --host
# Runs on http://localhost:5173
```

### Demo Flow
1. Open http://localhost:5173
2. Enter `https://github.com/pallets/flask` (pre-filled)
3. Click **🚀 Analyze** — watch the multi-agent progress overlay
4. Explore **Dashboard** → **Code Review** → **CEO Report**

